  "faq_q1": "What is Coupony?",
  "faq_a1": "Coupony is an app that provides you with the best coupons, deals, and discounts from your favorite stores in one place.",
  "faq_q2": "How do I use a coupon?",
  "faq_a2": "After browsing available offers, tap on the coupon to copy it, then use it when making a purchase from the store, either online or in-store.",
  "faq_q3": "Is the app free?",
  "faq_a3": "Yes, Coupony is completely free. You can browse and use all coupons and offers without any fees.",
  "faq_q4": "How do I contact support?",
  "faq_a4": "You can reach us through the \"Contact Us\" page in the Help & Support section, or directly via WhatsApp.",
  "faq_q5": "Can I become a merchant?",
  "faq_a5": "Absolutely! You can register as a merchant from the profile page by tapping \"Become a Seller\" to create your store.",

  "faq_seller_q1": "How do I create my first offer?",
  "faq_seller_a1": "From your store dashboard, tap \"Add Offer\", fill in the offer details including discount percentage, validity period, and terms. Your offer will be reviewed before going live.",
  "faq_seller_q2": "How long does store approval take?",
  "faq_seller_a2": "Store approval typically takes 24-48 hours. You'll receive a notification once your store is approved and ready to publish offers.",
  "faq_seller_q3": "Are there any fees for sellers?",
  "faq_seller_a3": "Currently, Coupony is free for all sellers. We may introduce premium features in the future, but basic store and offer management will remain free.",
  "faq_seller_q4": "How do I track my offer performance?",
  "faq_seller_a4": "Your dashboard provides detailed analytics including views, coupon usage, and customer engagement. You can track performance for each offer individually.",
  "faq_seller_q5": "Can I edit or delete published offers?",
  "faq_seller_a5": "Yes! You can edit offer details or delete offers anytime from your store management page. Changes to active offers take effect immediately.",

  "guide_step1_title": "Create an Account",
  "guide_step1_desc": "Register a new account using your email or enter as a guest to browse offers.",
  "guide_step2_title": "Browse Offers",
  "guide_step2_desc": "Explore the latest offers and coupons from stores near you or based on your interests.",
  "guide_step3_title": "Choose a Coupon",
  "guide_step3_desc": "Tap on the offer you like to view coupon details and available discount.",
  "guide_step4_title": "Copy the Code",
  "guide_step4_desc": "Copy the discount code with a single tap and use it when shopping.",
  "guide_step5_title": "Enjoy the Discount",
